thread.title: Bernard Reid

author: Bernard Reid
title: Bernard Reid
text: The cover I ordered was reasonably priced and because my phone is not the most recent model (in fact, it's bloody old), it was not available at local phone outlets. Because the cover I wanted was for an older phone I was a bit sceptical that the right item would be delivered but was pleasantly surprised that what I wanted actually turned up. I ordered the cover at approximately 11.00 pm on Sunday night and it was delivered to me on the following Tuesday morning. I would definitely use this company again.
